Third-party components
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This product bundles or links the following third-party components. Their own
licences apply to them and are not superseded by the Apache License above. See
docs/third_party.md for the full table, versions and linkage details.

  * Qt 6 — LGPL v3, DYNAMICALLY linked. The Qt libraries are shipped as separate
    DLLs beside the executable and may be replaced by the user, as LGPL v3 §4
    requires. No Qt sources are modified.

  * NTIA Irregular Terrain Model (ITM / Longley-Rice) — public domain (a work of
    the United States Government). Vendored unmodified in third_party/ntia_itm.

  * GDAL (MIT/X), GeographicLib (MIT), nlohmann/json (MIT), libzip (BSD-3),
    SQLite (public domain), zlib (zlib licence), GoogleTest (BSD-3, tests only).

  * ITU-R P.452 digital refractivity maps (resources/data/N050.TXT, DN50.TXT) —
    ITU-R Recommendation data files, redistributed as required to implement
    Recommendation ITU-R P.617-5.

  * resources/terrain/*.dt0 — derived from NASA SRTM (public domain) using
    tools/make_dted; provenance is marked in-app.

